_sName: All ICS CS:Source maps in one
_sText: This map pack contains all my 6 original maps + 2 remodified versions for assasination (VIP) mode for Counter-Strike Source All the maps contain multiple routes, nice details, 64 spawns by default, great framerate (fps) and they are made by a gamer to gamers. Large communities like UKCS and KIFFERSTUEBCHEN.DE also have some of these maps on their servers . Maps included inside are: - de_varasto v3 - de_hiekka v3 - de_tehdas v2 - cs_isku - de_slummi - de_syksy + - as_hiekka (VIP ver) - as_isku (VIP ver) To get VIP maps working as intended, you need a sourcemod plugin for it (this one) Maps created 2008-2011 by ICS http://www.ics-base.net - you can find more maps from there to other games too.
